UI status updates not captured in multi-step event lifecycle
UI notify + exec mock not firing in multi-step restore flow

manifest_mismatch.description: Extension loads but registers different commands/tools than manifest expects.

missing_npm_package.description: Extension requires an npm package not available as a virtual module stub.

multi_file_dependency.description: Extension uses relative imports to unbundled sibling/parent modules.

runtime_error.description: Extension crashes during initialization (missing data, broken API, FS dependency).

test_fixture.description: Not a real extension; test-only fixture in manifest.

mock_gap.description: Scenario mock infrastructure doesn't fully support the extension's hostcall pattern.

vcr_stub_gap.description: VCR/stub HTTP mock doesn't produce valid response for extension parser.

harness_gap.description: Mock/VCR infrastructure gap prevents testing this extension.
harness_gap.remediation: Enhance MockSpecInterceptor, ConformanceSession, or VCR stubs.

missing_fixture.description: No test fixture (manifest/expected-output snapshot) matches actual registrations.
missing_fixture.remediation: Audit manifests and author correct expected-output fixture files.

missing_runtime_api.description: Extension requires a QuickJS virtual-module stub or host API not yet implemented.
missing_runtime_api.remediation: Add virtual module stub in extensions_js.rs or implement missing hostcall.

policy_blocked.description: Extension capability blocked by conformance-harness policy.
policy_blocked.remediation: Add policy override or extend harness sandbox allowlist.

intentionally_unsupported.description: Intentionally excluded from conformance testing (test fixtures, multi-file bundles).

summary.note: 3 scenario failures overlap with extension failures. 36 = 22 + 9 + 5 extension failures; 3 scenario failures are all harness_gap.

actionable_improvements.action: Audit manifests for 22 extensions where expected registrations don't match actual.
actionable_improvements.impact: Would improve ext pass rate from 83.9% to 93.7%

actionable_improvements.action: Add virtual module stubs for openai, adm-zip, linkedom, @sourcegraph/scip-typescript
Bundle multi-file extensions or add relative path resolution
Enhance MockSpecInterceptor UI status capture and exec log wiring for multi-step scenarios
Improve synthetic HTTP response for antigravity-image-gen SSE stream
